{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2301986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "把21改成3，结论显而易见", "timestamp": 1629226703, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302018, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "枚举法", "timestamp": 1629227201, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302034, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "考虑组合问题不涉及排列。从一到二十一编个号小明是二十一，不考虑小明时二十个人排队。任取一种情况分析，小明有两个选择。在两对人数不相等时小明的选择使在人多人少的概率相同，在两对人数相等时小明总是在人多一对。", "timestamp": 1629227455, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302065, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302034, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 考虑排列时，仍然二十个人先排好，小明插空，在人多的队里有更多的空。", "timestamp": 1629228457, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302097, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2301986, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 大胆点，改成1也是一样的🐶", "timestamp": 1629231016, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302065, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 对对，就是这样。大于二分之一——因为“人多的队人多”。", "timestamp": 1629231059, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302205, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302097, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 1的话过于退化", "timestamp": 1629245961, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302416, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "换个想法 2K+1局K胜的比赛，你拥有永远不败的实力，那么你队伍获胜的概率当然会更高", "timestamp": 1629250243, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302836, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1111, "w": 1080}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302416, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 虽然你说得对，但是听你的话我总能想到这个", "timestamp": 1629255175, "type": "image", "url": "o5/o5agmueuzt5lkotpm6ljpj4z3rqq5cq5.jpeg"}, {"cid": 2302842, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302836, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 什么叫风险对冲啊", "timestamp": 1629255234, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2302847, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 441982, "reply_to": 2302842, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 《如何永远不败》", "timestamp": 1629255304, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 441982, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "#每晚问题\n某办事处有两个功能完全相同的窗口，每个来此办事处的人可以任选一个窗口排队。办事处今早开门之前，已有小明和其他20个人共21人前来等候。开门时，这21人分别独立等可能地选择一个窗口排队。因为总人数是奇数，总会有一个队伍比另一队人多。\n判断：小明在人多的那一队的概率大于二分之一。", "timestamp": 1629226166, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1629255303, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"是": 81, "不是": 14, "瓜": 15}, "vote_options": ["是", "不是", "瓜"]}}}